				<outline text="Hey, remember when the House Democrats were going to make all these shady people testify and instead nothing happened? @GaslitNation launched a four-week Patreon bonus series to look at where they are now -- and where they should be! Join and listen here: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/bonus-81-where-1-53745199&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt; https://t.co/xUUVANjyYX" type="tweet" created="Wed, 21 Jul 2021 12:00:36 GMT" tweetId="1417816778194014211" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1417816778194014211" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
