				<outline text="New @gaslitnation is out! We kick off our summer interview series with a talk with Bill Browder about global kleptocracy, Kremlin threats, and Western complicity &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/red-notice-full-53743587&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 21 Jul 2021 11:55:57 GMT" tweetId="1417815609497300992" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1417815609497300992" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
