			<outline text="July 18" type="calendarDay" name="18" >
				<outline text="Curious what results would be in other countries, like Israel, where Netanyahu DID want to microchip people in reaction to covid: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.jpost.com/israel-news/benjamin-netanyahu-suggests-to-microchip-kids-slammed-by-experts-627381&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt; https://t.co/8YCn4rMEsn" type="tweet" created="Sun, 18 Jul 2021 23:19:57 GMT" tweetId="1416900580644204551" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1416900580644204551" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="Approaching the two-month anniversary of this tweet of basic facts, which resulted in harassment of me by bot-brained mobs insisting there was a “secret plan” and all would be rectified soon 🙃 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1397022075215351809&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Sun, 18 Jul 2021 15:28:13 GMT" tweetId="1416781865244139520" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1416781865244139520" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="My mom found my beloved collection of Garbage Pail Kids, which I had cleverly hidden from my first-grade teacher in a container marked &quot;Pencil Box&quot; &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1416765202792554497/photo/1&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Sun, 18 Jul 2021 14:22:01 GMT" tweetId="1416765202792554497" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1416765202792554497" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
					<outline text="Hello old friends! &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1416765730565984261/photo/1&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Sun, 18 Jul 2021 14:24:07 GMT" tweetId="1416765730565984261" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1416765730565984261" inReplyToId="1416765202792554497" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
					</outline>
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 16" type="calendarDay" name="16" >
				<outline text="Oh this is sad. I have good childhood memories of him and of my own kids loving him on “Yo Gabba Gabba”. Unique and funny and beloved by multiple generations. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/franklinleonard/status/1416185034113945602&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Sat, 17 Jul 2021 00:03:26 GMT" tweetId="1416186745197039624" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1416186745197039624" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="Nov 2019 @gaslitnation thread on how the publishing industry functions as a means to protect the criminal elite and bury incriminating information until it’s too late to act on it &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1194633383336280070&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 16 Jul 2021 15:53:06 GMT" tweetId="1416063348567859211" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1416063348567859211" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="When you are contending with an aspiring autocracy that attempts to rewrite history as it unfolds, it’s important to have an archive that provides chronology and context — to know who knew what when. @AndreaChalupa and I created that at @gaslitnation. &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.gaslitnationpod.com/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 16 Jul 2021 14:54:01 GMT" tweetId="1416048480523591682" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1416048480523591682" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
					<outline text="I used to say that info on Trump and his criminal cohort is in the public domain. That’s no longer true: now it’s paywalled. @GaslitNation will continue to provide *free* shows and transcripts to all. But we could use support from those who can afford it: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/gaslit&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 16 Jul 2021 14:57:58 GMT" tweetId="1416049476138147840" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1416049476138147840" inReplyToId="1416048480523591682" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="A thread from the @gaslitnation episode, “The Good Germans”: &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1303687063712280577&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 16 Jul 2021 14:43:55 GMT" tweetId="1416045938372751372" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1416045938372751372" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
					<outline text="Another thread on “The Good Germans” of the USA. They’re still there, profiteering off your pain. Call them out for what they are. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1303674342774116352&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 16 Jul 2021 14:46:29 GMT" tweetId="1416046583964213250" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1416046583964213250" inReplyToId="1416045938372751372" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
					</outline>
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 15" type="calendarDay" name="15" >
				<outline text="&quot;If you don’t know these things happened, their bare recitation can seem shocking, aggressive, simplistic, or wrong.&quot; &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/KatzOnEarth/status/1415493652109881345&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 16:29:07 GMT" tweetId="1415710026778300417" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1415710026778300417" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
