				<outline text="Commit crime. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/motowngirl4/status/1415434740031762440&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 14 Jul 2021 22:20:34 GMT" tweetId="1415436082490056704" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1415436082490056704" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="“The FBI was warned about his horrific abuse and did nothing” should really be the motto of the FBI &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/senblumenthal/status/1415432870865391616&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 14 Jul 2021 22:13:11 GMT" tweetId="1415434224367198212" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1415434224367198212" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="The groundwork being laid for the future is quicksand" type="tweet" created="Wed, 14 Jul 2021 18:54:15 GMT" tweetId="1415384163977469953" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1415384163977469953" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="New @gaslitnation bonus episode is up! Join on Patreon to hear it: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/bonus-leave-53679065&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;

Our regular weekly episode, as always, is free to all, so check that out too. https://t.co/Af37dGwl8J" type="tweet" created="Wed, 14 Jul 2021 15:39:36 GMT" tweetId="1415335176981254152" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1415335176981254152" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="Thread from Feb 2021 on Trump and his insular network of criminal elites who organized the Capitol attacks &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1362038905730719749&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 14 Jul 2021 14:48:00 GMT" tweetId="1415322189574836234" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1415322189574836234" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="&quot;It's the sense of having a government that seems to welcome death; a government that has abdicated even the pretense of working for its citizens or caring if they live or die.&quot;

I wrote that in 2019 about Missouri. We're still living it now. 
https://t.co/IpjLWPjBH8 https://t.co/0eFZC88h7r" type="tweet" created="Wed, 14 Jul 2021 14:28:58 GMT" tweetId="1415317402074681350" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1415317402074681350" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
