			<outline text="July 9" type="calendarDay" name="09" >
				<outline text="New @gaslitnation transcript is out! Read about complicity, corruption and and the climate crisis in &quot;The United States of Exxon&quot; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.gaslitnationpod.com/episodes-transcripts-20/2021/7/7/the-united-states-of-exxon&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt; https://t.co/J6hfqMHYbd" type="tweet" created="Fri, 09 Jul 2021 16:47:16 GMT" tweetId="1413540266712174597" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1413540266712174597" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
