			<outline text="July 8" type="calendarDay" name="08" >
				<outline text="I went on a hike at night in Missouri to look at bats &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1413127910416916484/photo/1&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 08 Jul 2021 13:28:43 GMT" tweetId="1413127910416916484" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1413127910416916484" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 7" type="calendarDay" name="07" >
				<outline text="&quot;Gaslit Nation is resisting the paywall tide because we believe the public should not have to pay to stay informed about various apocalyptic developments.&quot;

Keep @gaslitnation accessible to all by joining our Patreon! &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/gaslit&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt; https://t.co/egQwe4L03y" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 14:58:30 GMT" tweetId="1412788120605581312" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1412788120605581312" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="&quot;The politicians -- whether Trump, Manchin or Sinema -- that we're up against are just the bouncing clowns. They have behind them much darker forces who are the real enemy. We see this clearly with Exxon.&quot; -- @AndreaChalupa on @gaslitnation &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/united-states-of-53394709&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 13:45:31 GMT" tweetId="1412769753127600131" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1412769753127600131" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
					<outline text="&quot;The long-time CEO of Exxon was Rex Tillerson, Trump's Sec of State. Exxon now has weekly meetings with Joe Manchin and has made in-roads to Biden. Why do you think Biden is breaking so many of his campaign promises? Part of the reason is Exxon.&quot; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/united-states-of-53394709&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 13:51:50 GMT" tweetId="1412771342944964616" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1412771342944964616" inReplyToId="1412769753127600131" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
						<outline text="&quot;Republicans turned the US into a struggling democracy, stressed by a losing war against corruption. Republicans held the door open for the Kremlin and they walked right in. The GOP literally sold our country for profit.&quot; -- @AndreaChalupa on @gaslitnation &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/united-states-of-53394709&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 13:53:31 GMT" tweetId="1412771764602540034" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1412771764602540034" inReplyToId="1412771342944964616" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
							<outline text="&quot;Russia welcomes climate change because the melting ice opens up the Arctic for ships and drilling and lets them become an agricultural powerhouse. Exxon and the GOP see a future where they thrive in the climate crisis, a future of disaster capitalism.&quot; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/united-states-of-53394709&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 13:55:57 GMT" tweetId="1412772379479134212" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1412772379479134212" inReplyToId="1412771764602540034" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
								<outline text="&quot;Fox News is launching a weather service that will likely peddle another big lie: that a hot, uninhabitable planet is good for you. It'll be like Soviet Pravda for the weather.&quot; -- @AndreaChalupa on @gaslitnation &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/united-states-of-53394709&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 13:58:17 GMT" tweetId="1412772963234062337" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1412772963234062337" inReplyToId="1412772379479134212" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
									<outline text="&quot;The handling of covid-19 was a test for the climate crisis: 'Let's just let mass death happen, let's not give people resources or healthcare or coherent advice, let's see if anyone is held accountable when they die.' 

&quot;And no one was held accountable.&quot; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/united-states-of-53394709&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 14:07:17 GMT" tweetId="1412775231475814401" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1412775231475814401" inReplyToId="1412772963234062337" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
									</outline>
								</outline>
							</outline>
						</outline>
					</outline>
				<outline text="&quot;The crimes for which Weisselberg was charged are the same crimes that Ivanka Trump committed. We know she's committed tax fraud; this information has been in the public domain for months. Why is she still walking free?&quot; -- @AndreaChalupa on @gaslitnation &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/united-states-of-53394709&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 12:48:00 GMT" tweetId="1412755277431119875" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1412755277431119875" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
					<outline text="&quot;The Trump Org has always run on a culture of corruption and Trump and Ivanka brought that culture to the White House, where it flourished at the cost of countless American lives.&quot; -- @AndreaChalupa on @gaslitnation &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/united-states-of-53394709&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 12:52:43 GMT" tweetId="1412756464247185411" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1412756464247185411" inReplyToId="1412755277431119875" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
						<outline text="&quot;Aspiring autocrats take advantage of the rotting culture of nepotism already employed by the officials tasked to hold them accountable. It was DA Cy Vance Jr, son of former Secretary of State Cy Vance, who originally let Ivanka off the hook in 2012.&quot; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/united-states-of-53394709&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 12:57:06 GMT" tweetId="1412757569102401542" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1412757569102401542" inReplyToId="1412756464247185411" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
							<outline text="&quot;The Trump family is a straight-up mafia family. Watch if Ivanka gets indicted. If she doesn't, then we're in trouble, and the men and women who should be protecting us are once again failing to do so.&quot; -- @AndreaChalupa on @gaslitnation &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/united-states-of-53394709&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 13:02:55 GMT" tweetId="1412759031639314435" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1412759031639314435" inReplyToId="1412757569102401542" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
								<outline text="&quot;There are photos of Allen Weisselberg meant to look like a perp walk, but he's not handcuffed. He's holding his own handcuffs in his hands. Amazing symbolism of the Trump Crime Cult's hijacking of the rule of law.&quot; -- @gaslitnation &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/united-states-of-53394709&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 13:08:16 GMT" tweetId="1412760377809588230" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1412760377809588230" inReplyToId="1412759031639314435" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
								</outline>
							</outline>
						</outline>
					</outline>
				<outline text="On Dem refusal to prosecute criminal elites for Jan 6: &quot;There is an instigator and an accomplice, and after six months if you cannot clearly see the complicity of the accomplice, it’s because you do not want to.&quot; -- @gaslitnation &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/united-states-of-53394709&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 12:21:18 GMT" tweetId="1412748557405327366" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1412748557405327366" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
					<outline text="&quot;What kind of a country does not defend itself against an open attack against its own Capitol, an attack where bombs were planted and the attackers openly declared their intent was to murder members of Congress?&quot; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/united-states-of-53394709&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 12:23:19 GMT" tweetId="1412749064349925380" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1412749064349925380" inReplyToId="1412748557405327366" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
						<outline text="&quot;What kind of government does nothing to prosecute a Kremlin asset backed by a transnational crime syndicate who has been actively, and successfully, trying to destroy this country from within for personal profit and to appease foreign backers?&quot; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/united-states-of-53394709&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 12:24:41 GMT" tweetId="1412749411487301635" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1412749411487301635" inReplyToId="1412749064349925380" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
							<outline text="&quot;What kind of country does nothing when its elections are attacked by that same syndicate and when voting rights are destroyed by that syndicate’s court appointees?

&quot;The kind of country whose elites do not care if it exists anymore.&quot; -- @gaslitnation  &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/united-states-of-53394709&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 12:25:47 GMT" tweetId="1412749686281322500" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1412749686281322500" inReplyToId="1412749411487301635" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
								<outline text="&quot;The behavior of the Democrats acting as accomplices to the criminal GOP is reminiscent of how Soviet elites behaved in the late 1980s and early 1990s. They plotted for the aftermath and decided how to divvy up resources.&quot; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/united-states-of-53394709&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 12:27:07 GMT" tweetId="1412750022098231296" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1412750022098231296" inReplyToId="1412749686281322500" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
									<outline text="&quot;They covered up massive crimes with facile symbolism and hollow words. The will of the people was irrelevant to them and ideology was only a mask for power. They didn’t believe in anything except preserving their own wealth, power and impunity.&quot; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/united-states-of-53394709&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 12:28:43 GMT" tweetId="1412750423300231168" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1412750423300231168" inReplyToId="1412750022098231296" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
										<outline text="&quot;For these criminal elites, autocracy may be simply a stepping stone to partitioning the US into smaller, more manageable autocratic oligarch fiefdoms. They may see a partitioned US as advantageous as the climate crisis ravages land and resources.&quot; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/united-states-of-53394709&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 12:34:38 GMT" tweetId="1412751911556616199" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1412751911556616199" inReplyToId="1412750423300231168" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
										</outline>
									</outline>
								</outline>
							</outline>
						</outline>
					</outline>
				<outline text="New @gaslitnation is out! This week we discuss the climate crisis and who benefits, why Ivanka is as guilty as Weisselberg and should be indicted, the ramifications of your own government refusing to investigate an attempt to overthrow itself, more: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.patreon.com/posts/united-states-of-53394709&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 07 Jul 2021 12:18:22 GMT" tweetId="1412747820701040641" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1412747820701040641" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				</outline>
