			<outline text="July 2" type="calendarDay" name="02" >
				<outline text="Cosby lived across the street from Jeffrey Epstein. Cosby's lawyer, Castor, is enmeshed in the same crime cult, even representing Trump at his second impeachment hearing. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/KlasfeldReports/status/1411058662420910080&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 02 Jul 2021 20:39:16 GMT" tweetId="1411061935970426888" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1411061935970426888" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="New @gaslitnation transcript is out! Read &quot;Why Are the Democrats Keeping Louis DeJoy?&quot;, which also touches on the Trump Org investigation, here: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.gaslitnationpod.com/episodes-transcripts-20/2021/6/30/why-are-the-democrats-keeping-louis-dejoy&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt; https://t.co/0FFise3c2Y" type="tweet" created="Fri, 02 Jul 2021 14:01:28 GMT" tweetId="1410961827064958984" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1410961827064958984" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="July 1" type="calendarDay" name="01" >
				<outline text="Thread &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/elienyc/status/1410731188520579086&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 01 Jul 2021 23:28:14 GMT" tweetId="1410742070520676358" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1410742070520676358" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="I'm sick and unfortunately won't be there tonight. But I strongly urge people to attend and to support the other speakers. I'm grateful to the organizers and hope to be at the next event. https://t.co/qRz5bznIVO" type="tweet" created="Thu, 01 Jul 2021 13:22:38 GMT" tweetId="1410589667792195586" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1410589667792195586" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="This is a massive crisis in an era of rising autocracy and widespread disinformation and propaganda campaigns, especially those seeking to bury or rewrite history https://t.co/dQZLMDLyvE" type="tweet" created="Thu, 01 Jul 2021 13:20:18 GMT" tweetId="1410589078802898946" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1410589078802898946" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
