		<outline text="June 2021" type="calendarMonth" name="june2021" >
			<outline text="June 30" type="calendarDay" name="30" >
				<outline text="My grandma listened to then watched this show for 70 years! I got to hear about this pivotal day in the history of her “stories” many times lol https://t.co/SIHXqbKmQV" type="tweet" created="Wed, 30 Jun 2021 21:51:26 GMT" tweetId="1410355319797071872" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1410355319797071872" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="&quot;What we have is a multi-decade criminal plot that a bankruptcy is not going to deter at this point, because Trump is now operating with special status as a malevolent, post-presidential demagogue who has basically been declared above the law by Garland.&quot; https://t.co/PqORSLGiVl" type="tweet" created="Wed, 30 Jun 2021 16:36:41 GMT" tweetId="1410276112584921092" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1410276112584921092" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
					<outline text="&quot;We see once again the entanglement of state crime, corporate crime, and organized crime. Unfortunately we have a virtuoso at granting elite criminal impunity running the Trump Org investigation -- DA Cyrus Vance, who let off Don Jr, Ivanka, Epstein, etc&quot; https://t.co/PqORSLGiVl" type="tweet" created="Wed, 30 Jun 2021 16:38:49 GMT" tweetId="1410276650135269381" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1410276650135269381" inReplyToId="1410276112584921092" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
						<outline text="&quot;It is in the best interest of this country for these dangerous individuals to be quickly prosecuted. It's not personal, not about revenge. It's about the fact that organized crime infiltrated every major institution and body of the US.&quot; -- @gaslitnation https://t.co/PqORSLGiVl" type="tweet" created="Wed, 30 Jun 2021 16:40:32 GMT" tweetId="1410277079850041344" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1410277079850041344" inReplyToId="1410276650135269381" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
							<outline text="&quot;This isn't limited to Trump. You see the same phenomenon with Epstein/Maxwell, these tentacles reaching big tech, universities, research centers. Our institutions had decades to stop it. Instead they too were infiltrated and coopted.&quot; --@gaslitnation https://t.co/PqORSLGiVl" type="tweet" created="Wed, 30 Jun 2021 16:43:10 GMT" tweetId="1410277743825244162" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1410277743825244162" inReplyToId="1410277079850041344" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
							</outline>
						</outline>
					</outline>
				<outline text="Thread on Louis DeJoy, destroyer of the postal service, and Biden's refusal to fire the Board member who is protecting DeJoy https://t.co/JJ2ZmpqoxS" type="tweet" created="Wed, 30 Jun 2021 16:34:27 GMT" tweetId="1410275548597784578" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1410275548597784578" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="&quot;People thought that one of the most basic things we would get with a Biden presidency would be Louis DeJoy being replaced with someone who actually cares about preserving and protecting USPS. That has not been the case.&quot; -- @gaslitnation https://t.co/PqORSLGiVl" type="tweet" created="Wed, 30 Jun 2021 16:11:41 GMT" tweetId="1410269821648973825" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1410269821648973825" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
					<outline text="&quot;DeJoy is still there. And that is a horrific testament to the fact that Americans have not been getting the accountability that we so sorely need, and that people are continuing to suffer from this ongoing lack of accountability.&quot; -- @gaslitnation https://t.co/PqORSLGiVl" type="tweet" created="Wed, 30 Jun 2021 16:13:41 GMT" tweetId="1410270325665841155" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1410270325665841155" inReplyToId="1410269821648973825" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
						<outline text="&quot;It should be easy to remove DeJoy. Biden replaced some members from the Board of Governors so the Board could ostensibly remove DeJoy. But Biden will not replace DeJoy supporter Ron Bloom, who is connected to Jared Kusher.&quot; --@gaslitnation https://t.co/PqORSLGiVl" type="tweet" created="Wed, 30 Jun 2021 16:17:48 GMT" tweetId="1410271358496411654" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1410271358496411654" inReplyToId="1410270325665841155" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
							<outline text="&quot;Bloom, a Democrat, has worked for Brookfield Asset Management since 2016. Brookfield is the company that orchestrated Kushner's shady deal with Qatar to bail him out on his 666 5th Avenue project in 2018. Bloom is now a DeJoy loyalist.&quot; -- @gaslitnation https://t.co/PqORSLGiVl" type="tweet" created="Wed, 30 Jun 2021 16:21:55 GMT" tweetId="1410272395533983749" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1410272395533983749" inReplyToId="1410271358496411654" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
								<outline text="Here's more information on Bloom, Kushner, DeJoy, and Biden: https://t.co/GCp1ROoes9" type="tweet" created="Wed, 30 Jun 2021 16:22:24 GMT" tweetId="1410272518624235527" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1410272518624235527" inReplyToId="1410272395533983749" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
									<outline text="&quot;What is disturbing here isn't just Biden's refusal to fire Bloom and DeJoy, but the broader direction we're headed regardless of which party holds the reins of power. The goal remains to strip the US down and sell it for parts.&quot; -- @gaslitnation https://t.co/PqORSLGiVl" type="tweet" created="Wed, 30 Jun 2021 16:26:19 GMT" tweetId="1410273505481052170" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1410273505481052170" inReplyToId="1410272518624235527" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
										<outline text="&quot;There are differences in how the GOP and Democrats package the privatization and elimination of basic services. Dems call it 'asset recycling.' Watch for that phrase. The difference between Dems and GOP is just the level of accelerationalism and sadism.&quot; https://t.co/PqORSLGiVl" type="tweet" created="Wed, 30 Jun 2021 16:29:32 GMT" tweetId="1410274314608328710" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1410274314608328710" inReplyToId="1410273505481052170" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
										</outline>
									</outline>
								</outline>
							</outline>
						</outline>
					</outline>
				<outline text="New @gaslitnation is out! Louis DeJoy and the plot to strip the US down and sell it for parts, the latest on the Trump Organization investigation, Giuliani and what a “Trump lawyer” actually does, more https://t.co/36QeN4ysQz" type="tweet" created="Wed, 30 Jun 2021 11:21:22 GMT" tweetId="1410196760648167428" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1410196760648167428" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="June 29" type="calendarDay" name="29" >
				<outline text="What worries me about MO and NV being top two in Delta is that both have cities that are major tourist attractions where people are crammed in close quarters: Vegas and Branson (which is in the region of MO with highest rate of infection). Seem likely pathways to spread across US https://t.co/B4kOr9Oxny" type="tweet" created="Wed, 30 Jun 2021 00:35:36 GMT" tweetId="1410034249730830337" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1410034249730830337" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
