Keep our podcast independent and accessible to all by supporting us on Patreon! https://t.co/Na8D7sa2BC" type="tweet" created="Wed, 30 Jun 2021 00:26:17 GMT" tweetId="1410031903453888515" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1410031903453888515" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
