				<outline text="&quot;To millionaire elites, many of whom already had an apocalyptic bent, a depopulated world is not a tragedy but an opportunity -- and certainly easier to manage as they insulate themselves from the ravages of a literally scorched earth.&quot; 

https://t.co/IpjLWPjBH8 https://t.co/1xtFErjudR" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 14:55:35 GMT" tweetId="1409525894218240009" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1409525894218240009" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
