				<outline text="“Missouri is a harbinger for the rest of the country.” https://t.co/oQ6B1XJxrk" type="tweet" created="Mon, 21 Jun 2021 11:37:07 GMT" tweetId="1406939232048910336" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1406939232048910336" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
