			<outline text="June 14" type="calendarDay" name="14" >
				<outline text="Biden and the board need to get rid of Louis DeJoy, who should be under investigation for election tampering and perjury, not running USPS. Congress members should be applying pressure. Instead we get &quot;mistakes were made&quot;-style statements like this on Twitter. https://t.co/z7mbZQxe8U" type="tweet" created="Mon, 14 Jun 2021 16:23:18 GMT" tweetId="1404474536377171971" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1404474536377171971" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
