					<outline text="Now lock Trump up, replace Diane Feinstein with Jello Biafra (long overdue!), buy my book instead of books by criminal elites, and maybe we'll get back on track https://t.co/IpjLWPjBH8 https://t.co/LgkpzzcrNG" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 20:37:51 GMT" tweetId="1403451433807187975" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403451433807187975" inReplyToId="1403450764434067459" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
