				<outline text="Nearly a century ago, Jim the Wonder Dog predicted that I would interview fellow Marshall hometown hero @lynzforcongress about our fine state! Listen here: https://t.co/YgZqdkmDpB https://t.co/ZkAWJVX5MC" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 17:47:10 GMT" tweetId="1403408480778821637" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403408480778821637" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="&quot;In addition to being the dark money center of the US, Missouri is also the center of disinformation. We have radio stations in Kansas City owned by the Russian government spitting out propaganda. We had Rush Limbaugh in southern MO for generations.&quot; https://t.co/YgZqdkmDpB" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 17:32:10 GMT" tweetId="1403404704290377734" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403404704290377734" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
					<outline text="&quot;But the problem isn't just disinfo and dark money and bad media. It's that the Dems did not invest and do the work and create infrastructure to sustain long-term growth in MO. Now we are experiencing the fallout.&quot; -- @lynzforcongress https://t.co/YgZqdkmDpB" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 17:34:27 GMT" tweetId="1403405280617054210" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403405280617054210" inReplyToId="1403404704290377734" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="Thread on Eric Greitens, my twice-indicted former governor who is now running for Senate https://t.co/ljKVCLfTIk" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 17:25:28 GMT" tweetId="1403403020780638208" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403403020780638208" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="&quot;Eric Greitens talks about deploying with Navy SEALs in combat which is something he's never done. Veterans have come out and talked about his fraudulent claims in addition to all the crimes he's committed.&quot; -- Lindsey Simmons on @gaslitnation https://t.co/YgZqdkmDpB" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 17:13:20 GMT" tweetId="1403399965796442117" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403399965796442117" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
					<outline text="&quot;Greitens is back running for Senate because no one ever prosecuted him. He can still pretend to be 'the outsider' despite being the governor of Missouri previously. And people love him, they really do.&quot; -- @LynzforCongress on @gaslitnation https://t.co/YgZqdkmDpB" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 17:15:36 GMT" tweetId="1403400537987497992" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403400537987497992" inReplyToId="1403399965796442117" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
						<outline text="&quot;National Dem strategists think Greitens will have a Todd Akin moment and so they *want* him to run, but the GOP of 2012 is not the GOP of 2021. There is nothing so indecent that Republicans won't stand by you anymore.&quot; -- @LynzforCongress on @gaslitnation https://t.co/YgZqdkmDpB" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 17:17:28 GMT" tweetId="1403401005069438976" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403401005069438976" inReplyToId="1403400537987497992" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
							<outline text="&quot;If Eric Greitens becomes Senator, Missouri will be represented by:
1) A sexual assaulter stolen valor human who should be in prison
2) An insurrectionist domestic terror promoting counterfeit weasel&quot; -- @lynzforcongress https://t.co/YgZqdkmDpB" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 17:21:02 GMT" tweetId="1403401905347477505" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403401905347477505" inReplyToId="1403401005069438976" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
							</outline>
						</outline>
					</outline>
				<outline text="Thread on Josh Hawley from someone who knows! Listen to the full interview for more disturbing details: https://t.co/dy46H4Ieeb" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 17:05:47 GMT" tweetId="1403398065101357062" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403398065101357062" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
				<outline text="&quot;Joshua Hawley is a counterfeit Senator and a counterfeit human. He's a banker's son who went to a fancy school in KC, then Stanford, then Yale. Then he comes back and doesn't know what a flat-bed truck is. He wears flannel but it's from Brooks Brothers.&quot; https://t.co/YgZqdkmDpB" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 16:48:07 GMT" tweetId="1403393618619125769" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403393618619125769" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
					<outline text="&quot;There's a lack of respect for Joshua in rural MO. He's counterfeit and he's calculated. He lied about arguing the Hobby Lobby case in front of SCOTUS. There's zero chance he actually did the things he's been telling Missourians he did.&quot; -- @gaslitnation https://t.co/YgZqdkmDpB" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 16:51:55 GMT" tweetId="1403394575046168578" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403394575046168578" inReplyToId="1403393618619125769" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
						<outline text="&quot;The thing you need to know about Joshua is that he's a true believer in Christian fascism. He believes the only way to be a good politician is to create a government in the way the Lord wants him to. He talks a lot about control over the citizenry.&quot; https://t.co/YgZqdkmDpB" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 16:53:54 GMT" tweetId="1403395073589587969" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403395073589587969" inReplyToId="1403394575046168578" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
							<outline text="&quot;Hawley wants authoritarianism to thrive. We saw that from him on Jan 6 and we saw it before, and you'll continue to see that from him. It's not just an act. Ironically, he's *still* too counterfeit for the Trump base and they reject him.&quot; https://t.co/YgZqdkmDpB" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 16:56:22 GMT" tweetId="1403395697316093953" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403395697316093953" inReplyToId="1403395073589587969" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
								<outline text="&quot;Hawley is strongly tied to Peter Thiel. This tie goes back to his days at Stanford...Thiel maxxed out to him in the Senate race. That's one of those connections that people really need to investigate more.&quot; -- Lindsey Simmons on @gaslitnation https://t.co/YgZqdkmDpB" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 16:59:34 GMT" tweetId="1403396500043055104" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403396500043055104" inReplyToId="1403395697316093953" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
									<outline text="&quot;Hawley's interest in big tech is about shutting down sharing of videos showing abuses of power and the people's ability to communicate across broad expanses of geography. Authoritarianism is a lot more feasible under those circumstances.&quot; - @gaslitnation https://t.co/YgZqdkmDpB" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 17:02:07 GMT" tweetId="1403397143822487559" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403397143822487559" inReplyToId="1403396500043055104" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
									</outline>
								</outline>
							</outline>
						</outline>
					</outline>
				<outline text="&quot;Missouri has long been a pathway to worse things in national politics. Failure to recognize GOP autocracy in MO put the entire nation in jeopardy. Operatives that dealt in dark money in Missouri have their tentacles in Pence and Hawley.&quot; -- @gaslitnation https://t.co/YgZqdkmDpB" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 16:38:12 GMT" tweetId="1403391125155717126" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403391125155717126" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
					<outline text="&quot;In Missouri, things are made legal that violate federal law. People will say 'Well, they can't do that!' but here they only can't do something if you're willing to stand up and fight it in court.&quot; -- @LynzforCongress on @gaslitnation https://t.co/YgZqdkmDpB" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 16:42:26 GMT" tweetId="1403392191989530624" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403392191989530624" inReplyToId="1403391125155717126" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="&quot;In Missouri, we meet many of the metrics for a failed state. Failed states have limited resources, a lack of democracy, great income inequality, failing education systems, a legislative takeover that gerrymandered away the political opposition...&quot; https://t.co/YgZqdkmDpB" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 16:17:50 GMT" tweetId="1403385998185271303" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403385998185271303" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
					<outline text="&quot;Rural and urban Missouri have so much in common, but political rhetoric is often used to divide our situations. The struggles we're facing are similar and we would do a great service to work together.&quot; -- @LynzforCongress on @gaslitnation https://t.co/YgZqdkmDpB" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 16:20:48 GMT" tweetId="1403386745287290883" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403386745287290883" inReplyToId="1403385998185271303" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" >
						<outline text="&quot;In a failed state, the political and economic system is so weak that govt no longer has control: what we have instead is one political party in control. We have a one-party state in Missouri. The power of the people is diminished.&quot; -- @LynzforCongress https://t.co/YgZqdkmDpB" type="tweet" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 16:25:58 GMT" tweetId="1403388047127990274" urltweet="https://twitter.com/sarahkendzior/status/1403388047127990274" inReplyToId="1403386745287290883" tweetUserName="sarahkendzior" />
						</outline>
					</outline>
